relevant_findings.general: Alert and in no apparent distress
relevant_findings.ENT: Ears and nose without visible erythema, masses, or trauma. Oropharynx without visible lesion, erythema or exudate
relevant_findings.CV: Heart regular, no murmur, no S3, no S4. No JVD. No edema
relevant_findings.resp: Lungs clear to auscultation with good air movement bilaterally. Breathing is non-labored
relevant_findings.GI: Abdomen soft; has no TTP. Bowel sounds present. No HSM
relevant_findings.GU: No suprapubic fullness or tenderness to palpation
relevant_findings.MSK: Neck supple, moves all extremities, strength grossly full and symmetric bilaterally in all limbs
relevant_findings.neuro: Alert, oriented, face symmetric, gaze conjugate with EOMI, speech fluent, moves all limbs, sensation to light touch grossly intact throughout
